Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:01:00.71,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Podľa komiksov\NKousuke Fujishimu „You're Under Arrest”\N\Nvydaných vydavateľstvom\NKodansha\N\NAnglická adaptácia\NDark Horse Comics a Studio Proteus
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:56.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...ako leto so slnkom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.71,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ak máme odvahu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:03.88,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...pri 100 míľach v hodine...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:11.99,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...sa nám určite splnia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:07.86,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Producenti\NTeruo Miyahara\NTakashi Mooi\NKatsuhisa Yamamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:10.86,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Návrh postáv\NAtsuko Nakajima\N\NNávrh strojov\NToshiharu Murata
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:19.13,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pretože smútok je tá cesta\Nvedúca k úsmevom...{\i0}
